info.author: Thomas R. Ioerger

info.name: transit2
info.summary: TRANSIT2 is a tool for the analysis of Tn-Seq data. It provides an easy to use graphical interface and access to three different analysis methods that allow the user to determine essentiality in a single condition as well as between conditions.
